data.value: Places the foreground over the background.

data.value: Places the background beneath the foreground.

data.value: Clips the foreground to the shape of the background.

data.value: Clips the background to the shape of the foreground.

data.name: BlendMode_SrcOut_Description
data.value: Keeps the area outside the background for the foreground.

data.value: Keeps the area outside the foreground for the background.

data.name: BlendMode_SrcATop_Description
data.value: Places the foreground on top and keeps the background outside.

data.name: BlendMode_DstATop_Description
data.value: Places the background on top and keeps the foreground outside.

data.name: BlendMode_Xor_Description
data.value: Makes overlapping areas transparent, keeping non-overlapping areas.

data.name: BlendMode_Plus_Description
data.value: Adds the colors of the foreground and background.

data.name: BlendMode_Modulate_Description
data.value: Combines the colors of the foreground and background based on their transparency (alpha values).

data.name: BlendMode_Multiply_Description
data.value: Multiplies the RGB color values of the foreground and background, creating a darker effect.

data.name: BlendMode_Overlay_Description
data.value: Combines the foreground and background to enhance contrast.

data.name: BlendMode_Darken_Description
data.value: Keeps the darker color of the foreground or background.

data.name: BlendMode_Lighten_Description
data.value: Keeps the lighter color of the foreground or background.

data.name: BlendMode_ColorDodge_Description
data.value: Brightens the background by adding the foreground color.

data.name: BlendMode_ColorBurn_Description
data.value: Darkens the background by burning it with the foreground color.

data.name: BlendMode_HardLight_Description
data.value: Simulates a harsh spotlight effect to enhance contrast.

data.name: BlendMode_SoftLight_Description
data.value: Simulates a diffused spotlight for smoother lighting effects.

data.name: BlendMode_Hue_Description
data.value: Applies the foreground hue to the background's luminance and saturation.

data.name: BlendMode_Saturation_Description
data.value: Applies the foreground saturation to the background's hue and luminance.

data.name: BlendMode_Color_Description
data.value: Applies the foreground hue and saturation to the background's luminance.

data.name: BlendMode_Luminosity_Description
data.value: Applies the foreground luminance to the background's hue and saturation.

data.name: BlendMode_Screen_Description
data.value: Multiplies the inverted colors of the foreground and background, creating a lighter effect.
